snippet.title: World Building: Adding Technology in Your World
snippet.description:
Technology allows you to enhance aspects of your world, and whilst it is easy to think of technology from our world, you should consider what technologies have other races and worlds needed to develop to assist them in their way of life.  

Take for example, a bird race will not need to develop flying technology, but finer motor control technology can assist them especially if they do not have hands.

In this video we focus on the technology template that you can find on the World Anvil website, and we go through the process of what you should consider. This can be for any roleplaying system such as Dungeons and Dragons or even Starfinder.

Leave your comments down below on what ttrpg technologies you have come up with that have enhanced your worlds in your world building process.

In this video we focus on the technology template that you can find on the World Anvil website, and we go through the process of what you should consider. This can be for any roleplaying system such as Dungeons and Dragons or even Starfinder.
